window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The world is beginning to crack. Lucas will hold it togetherâ€”or die trying.</b></p> <p>The omen's demise is itself an omen of times to come. The king, long constrained by the goddess' rules, finally has the chance to exercise his power over the world. Lucas soon realizes that those ambitions don't just stop at one world.</p> <p>As reality crumbles apart around them, the king enacts his plan, and the goddess meddles as she pleases, it will take everything Centerpoint has to even survive, let alone win. Victory is a process, and Lucas will ensure that humanity lives to see it complete.</p> <p>No matter what it takes.</p>"; 
